    - rid: 8189697324969099383
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "They say a dragon was seen in the south... but that\u2019s probably
          just old Mirk after too much mead."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697324969099384
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "There\u2019s a tavern three days from here where no one speaks \u2014
          only hand signs and grunts. Best ale I\u2019ve ever had."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697324969099385
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: or just fall on your face.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697324969099386
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "They say if you walk around the old oak tree backwards at midnight,
          you\u2019ll see your future... "
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697324969099387
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "Somewhere past the marshes, there\u2019s a tree that sings lullabies.
          Creepy ones."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697324969099388
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: My cousin swears he saw a knight riding a giant boar. Either that,
          or he drank too much mushroom wine.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697324969099389
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'I''m looking for village chief. Do you know something about his missing?
          I''m looking for village chief. Do you know something about his missing? '
    - rid: 8189697324969099390
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Hey! Are you Jovan? His wife told me he has white hat and red jacket!
    - rid: 8189697324969099391
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Any rumours?
    - rid: 8189697324969099392
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: See you!
    - rid: 8189697324969099393
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Test flag
    - rid: 8189697324969099394
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'I''m not him! I just look like him because this is a demo version
          of game! I saw him leave through the south gate and then head east to forest. '
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697324969099395
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "I shouldn\u2019t be saying this\u2026 but I saw the chief meeting
          strangers outside the village walls."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697324969099396
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "They weren\u2019t merchants, that much I\u2019m sure. Looked more
          like bandits than traders."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697324969099397
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: That's all i know.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
